  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Following previous positive experience with CITA-RNPT of infected pacemakers, we suggest
      that CITA-RNPT can be administered prophylactically to patients prior to replacement of
      CIED, immun-compromised patients, and others.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
